<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Shleung</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-03 13:23:43</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I just got my Aegis today.  Very happy.  <BR>
I would like to share my experience here so that I hope the other who would like to do the quest can face less difficulties.<BR>
<BR>
1. There is a method to increase the spawn cycle.  I think many of you know that Grimrot is a 210 mins spawn (counting placeholders).  There is a method to increase the spawn rate so that u will have a better chance on spawning lord within the same timeframe.<BR>
However, I cannot post it here, if u really camp at there, u will notice it after camping 420 mins.<BR>
(Hints: before a previous patch, spawn is 21 mins cycle (counting placeholders as well), now is 210 mins, the method can reduce the spawn time to 60 mins)<BR>
<BR>
2. ABout faction.  I am very worry when I got both no drop quest items (I afraid fail) I barely increase my faction by donating money (certainly I kill putrid skeleton at ruins).<BR>
I am a cleric following Rodcet of Life, I get warmly after donating 100pp and 50pp more I can accept the quest.  But I know I still need more to receive the reward.  I keep donating money.<BR>
And finally, I only get increase in Priestsoflife faction but no other effect on other e.g. GuardofQeyons.  I know this cannot be a milestone and I note down the amount of money I spent.  After further giving 200pp in gp form, I tried the quest and SUCCEEDED.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
About other points, I think other have posted it.</font></td></tr></table>
