<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hi all,<BR>
Thanks for all the useful information.  I am currently camping Grimrott and have yet to have him spawn(though i got PH 3 times hehe shoulda let it despawn!) oh well.  A little helpful hint while raising faction.  Pulling out 2 bone chips or GP's can go really slow moveing the bar to 2 gp's then done.  Heres a hint.  Hold control while you click the pile of chips and only one will be withdrawn.  You can do this 2 times faster that adjusting your bar from 20 down to 2.  Thanks again for all the great posts.<BR>
<BR>
38th cleric of bristlebane on the Tallon Zek server</font></td></tr></table>
