<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Someone commented that the Aegis can not be recharged based on the NO DROP status.  This should not be a factor and here's my reasoning:<BR>
<BR>
1.  You can always give NO DROP items to NPCs<BR>
2.  The Squad Ring that you can get from a Rivervale quest<BR>
is also NO DROP and rechargeable.<BR>
<BR>
So - The question becomes - Has anyone had the nerve to hand it back after using the charge?    </font></td></tr></table>
